<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Portable Charger - CAD Design</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css"> 

    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #0b1221;
            --accent-blue: #3b82f6;
            --slate-grey: #161e2d;
            --sub-text: #94a3b8;
            --light-text: #f1f5f9;
        }

        body {
            background-color: var(--bg) !important;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
        }

        body::after {
            content: "";
            position: fixed;
            top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; bottom: 0;
            border: 12px solid #1e293b; 
            pointer-events: none; 
            z-index: 9999;
        }

        .scroll-wrapper {
            height: 100vh;
            width: 100%;
            overflow-y: scroll;
            scroll-snap-type: y mandatory;
            scrollbar-width: none; 
            -ms-overflow-style: none;
        }
        .scroll-wrapper::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }

        .project-step {
            min-height: 100vh;
            width: 100%;
            scroll-snap-align: start;
            scroll-snap-stop: always;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 80px 60px;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            background-color: var(--bg);
            position: relative;
        }

        .challenges-section {
            justify-content: flex-start !important;
            padding-top: 100px !important;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .centered-content-wrapper {
            max-width: 800px;
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .centered-title {
            font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem);
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--light-text);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #1e293b;
            padding-bottom: 15px;
            display: inline-block;
        }

        .challenges-description {
            margin: 0 auto;
            max-width: 650px;
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: var(--sub-text);
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .image-display-container {
            width: 100%;
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .static-content-box {
            background: transparent;
            border: none;
            box-shadow: none;
            color: var(--light-text);
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 800px;
            width: 90%;
            text-align: center;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        .static-content-box h1 {
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4.5rem);
        }

        .fade-line-container {
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 40px 0;
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 20px;
        }

        .fade-line {
            height: 1px;
            width: 60%;
            max-width: 600px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent 0%, var(--accent-blue) 50%, transparent 100%);
            opacity: 0.6;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .project-step { padding: 40px 20px; }
            body::after { border-width: 8px; }
            .centered-title { font-size: 2rem; }
            .fade-line { width: 80%; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="scroll-wrapper">
        
        <section class="project-step">
            <a href="/" class="btn-back-home">‚Üê Home</a>
            
            <div class="static-content-box">
                <h1 class="centered-title" style="border-bottom-color: var(--accent-blue);">CAD Modeling</h1>
                
                <p class="challenges-description" style="color: var(--accent-blue); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 0.9rem;">
                    Fusion 360
                </p>
                
                <div class="line-long" style="margin: 20px auto; width: 30%; background-color: var(--accent-blue); opacity: 0.4;"></div>
                
                <p class="challenges-description">
                    Developing the Blueprint for the Portable Charging Device.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="fade-line-container">
                <div class="fade-line"></div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="project-step challenges-section">
            <div class="centered-content-wrapper">
                <h1 class="centered-title">Container Design</h1>
                <p class="challenges-description">
                    Using sketches and patterns within Fusion 360, I was able to create a Container for the Device.
                    However, iteration one did not acount for sizing constraints of breakout boards.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="image-display-container">
                <div class="button-img" style="height: 50vh; width: 90%; background-image: url('/images/fusion.png');">
                    <div class="img-overlay">Container Model Preview</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="fade-line-container">
                <div class="fade-line"></div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="project-step challenges-section">
            <div class="centered-content-wrapper">
                <h1 class="centered-title">Physical Container</h1>
                <p class="challenges-description">
                    The physical container was 3D printed using an ABS filament with the P1S printer.
                    Future iterations will focus on developing the PCB to the CAD model to ensure proper fitment.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="image-display-container">
                <div class="button-img" style="height: 50vh; width: 90%; background-image: url('/images/physical-model-jpeg');">
                    <div class="img-overlay">Physical Container Preview</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

    </div>

</body>
</html>